dct_alternative_sm: Jerusalem cum suburbiis, prout tempore Christi floruit
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, places of historical interest; an imaginary plan of ancient Jerusalem at the time of Jesus Christ.
Includes explanatory text and index: Beschreibung der Statt Jerusalem, samt einer Erkärung was eine jede Ziffer Zahl in dem Abriss derselben bedeute.
Features illustrations of settlements and people.
Appears in Seutter's Atlas novus. Augsburg, 1745?
